an to postpone their trip and not go to the station.\\\"\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 405, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SNCF\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The operator said the Atlantic, Northern and Eastern high-speed lines were impacted, with damage caused to several of its facilities, adding that one of the acts was \\\"foiled\\\" in the east after SNCF agents scared off several individuals.\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Trains\", \"score\": 0.8581761903616311, \"rank\": 0.14798024643974853, \"text\": \"Northern\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Trains\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Trains\"}, {\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SNCF\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SNCF CEO Jean-Pierre Farandou told journalists on Friday that cables - which are there to ensure the security of train drivers - were set on fire and taken apart but that authorities \\\"do not know who is behind it.\\\"\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SNCF\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\"}, {\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dardenne_brothers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.973584764507024e-18, \"text\": \"Jean-Pierre\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dardenne_brothers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dardenne_brothers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An intelligence source told CNN that French intelligence services are \\\"fully mobilized\\\" to find those responsible.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1041, \"end\": 1044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.913451947906423e-12, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}, {\"begin\": 1050, \"end\": 1056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999989484254983, \"rank\": 9.110684516936634e-07, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The source added that \\\"these methods have been used by the far-left in the past\\\" but \\\"there is no evidence to tie today's actions to them.\\\"\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Travel on the affected lines is \\\"very disrupted,\\\" with the railway network needing to divert and cancel a large number of trains, SNCF said.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1399, \"end\": 1403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SNCF\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Disruptions - which it estimates could impact around 250,000 travelers today - were expected throughout the weekend, affecting 800,000 passengers, as work crews oversee repairs, it added.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Passengers milled around outside Paris' Gare du Nord train station and sat with their luggage on staircases as the disruption laid waste to their travel plans.\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1632, \"end\": 1637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.451762278853369e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Francoise, an 80-year-old from La Rochelle, is trying to get home and back to her nurse after medical treatment in Paris.\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1790, \"end\": 1801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Rochelle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9756064730601095e-18, \"text\": \"La Rochelle\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Rochelle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Rochelle\"}, {\"begin\": 1874, \"end\": 1879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.451762278853369e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told CNN she is preparing to wait another five hours in the forlorn hope of catching a train.\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1890, \"end\": 1893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.913451947906423e-12, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We did not need a day like this!\\\"\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 2013, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"she said.\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Rapha\\u00ebl, a SNCF user who has been waiting for his train at Montparnasse Station in the capital since 6 a.m. local time, told CNN affiliate BFMTV that \\\"people are a little exasperated.\\\"\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2047, \"end\": 2051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SNCF\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\"}, {\"begin\": 2161, \"end\": 2164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.913451947906423e-12, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}, {\"begin\": 2175, \"end\": 2180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFMTV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The R\\u00e9mi Train Centre Val de Loire said travel on its railway lines would be disrupted until at least Monday, with a fire near the tracks in Courtalain, northern France impacting services to Paris.\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2251, \"end\": 2256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loire\", \"score\": 0.9999999991978257, \"rank\": 8.019997258851909e-10, \"text\": \"Loire\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loire\"}, {\"begin\": 2363, \"end\": 2373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courtalain\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Courtalain\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courtalain\", \"dbpedia\": 