urce/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999964761628, \"rank\": 3.5239297596151274e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There would be no trains from Paris' Gare Montparnasse, however, until at least 1 p.m. local time, Christophe Fanichet - the CEO of SNCF Voyageurs - told reporters.\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 3016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2882, \"end\": 2887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.451762278853369e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2889, \"end\": 2906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_Montparnasse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gare Montparnasse\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_Montparnasse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_Montparnasse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eurostar, the high-speed train service that connects the United Kingdom with France, has been forced to cancel and divert trains due to the \\\"coordinated acts of malice,\\\" on French lines.\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3018, \"end\": 3026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999999998485691, \"rank\": 1.5125639391615338e-10, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}, {\"begin\": 3075, \"end\": 3089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9997473862221098, \"rank\": 0.0002409244468841233, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 30